section.def:
gambling
                (賭博) includes gaming, betting and
            bookmaking;

place
                (場所) includes any ship, aircraft or vehicle, and
            any spot on land or water;

subparagraph.content:
the organization and conduct of a game of amusement with prizes to be
                        conducted on premises licensed under section 4 of the Places of
                        Public Entertainment Ordinance (Cap. 172);

being used in or for or in
                        connexion
                        with gambling in such premises or place;
